\id 3JN - Yine NT (Piro) -Peru 2008 (DBL -2013) 
\h 3 Gwa 
\toc1 3 Tixinri Kpashiri Gwa Kirukate 
\toc2 3 Gwa 
\toc3 3Gwa 
\mt1 3 Tixinri Kpashiri Gwa Kirukate 
\c 1  
\s1 Galuklewlu 
\p  
\v 1 Tyenwa tsru kirukatni. 
\p Gishiniikaluru Kayo chinanupa, galikakni nushinikanru. 
\p  
\v 2 Nushinikanru, nagjigogneyegityi waneyapyi kigle gwashle psoluyako ga wa gichkopyi, wa kigle pixanshinikanutyawaka pixka.  
\v 3 Gi rixanu numuwpotuta wa rapokinitkana wumolene, wanna gipgujtayegityi wa wanepotuko pixinri, wa wane pixa gomkagitinri galikakpotunanu tokanchi.  
\v 4 Gi wa tye pnute tsru gimuwlu waneyno, nyijnakpiranyegityapna nwugenene wa galikaka potu tokanchi romkagitna. 
\s1 Kayo ruslaginri ralixkota 
\p  
\v 5 Nushinikanru, poyagkakachriyi pixa kamrutlu klunerukokta kamrurchi wa molchine chinanu ga wa pnu giyakatyachine chinanu koxa.  
\v 6 Wanna gipgujtatlu pushiniklewle gapatjetachinkaka getanu. Kigleru pkamrutanu wa pupxaka yaletanna Goyakalunu kgimuka.  
\v 7 Gi rixanu Geso giwaka chinanu rushpakna. Gikena rawyana payine.  
\v 8 Giyagni wixa gimkata yoptoretna wane gixachine, rukamrurewatanunepwuna galikakpotunanu tokanchiya. 
\s1 Riyotrigi gimaletna 
\p  
\v 9 Satu tokanchi nyonyegitna gapatjetachine, seyni Riyotrigi galuka tsru gitakletnachriwa wanna yegi; gi wa yoptotwu.  
\v 10 Giyagni wale kamrure wa kamrutanru nupgujtatanu wa wane nyinipa. Mugletu tokanchiya maleshawaka jigyegishatwu. Ga wa tyekaka gi wa poyagotyawalu, seyni gi waleko yoptotna wumolene ga wa galukayoptoletachine rumaleta. Wale giknokna gapatjetachinyegiya. 
\s1 Rimitri kiglepiranyegiru pejnuruneyako 
\p  
\v 11 Nushinikanru, gi wa pyimanru gektutu seyni wa kigleru galikaka. Kigleru kamrutachri walenwa Goyakalu giyakatyachri. Gektutu kamrutachri, gi wa Goyakalu reta.  
\v 12 Rimitri kiglepiranyegiru pejnuruneyako, ga wa galikakaya koxa. Ga wa wixa gipgujtatlu. Ga wa gixa gimatlu wupgujtalewle galikakpotunanu. 
\s1 Ralipre galukleta 
\p  
\v 13 Gixo waneyno nyonyegityapmakyi, seyni gi naluka yonyegletyi ksajgaluyma ga wa yonawapiyma.  
\v 14 Seyni giyampotu nkagwaka getletyi. Ga wa getgojkakachine wuynumsakakanu. 
\p  
\v 15 Giglewanshinikankaakalurupyi. Pumatjene galukyi. Ga wa pixa palukgiwakatanna pumatanune satkaka.